{
  "stem": "9665.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because Melitta was working for the Dutch government.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She could send me cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't sell them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I exchanged that for everything which was necessary when we liberated the north of Holland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we stayed in North [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Beverland ?] until-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so we went to North [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Beverland. ?] I would say what would have been in the months of October, November, 1944.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It could have been December.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In January, we were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In February, March, they moved us closer to-- how was that called?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Closer to the border of Rotterdam.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there, we had a bit of a downfall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of our guys picking up water and so on, they went on a mine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they died there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of my close friends died there, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Rodriguez. ?] And I have to have some water in between.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[DRINKS] And right-- And then we got, we got marching orders.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are going to liberate the north of Holland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the place where we lost a lot of men, I think-- and I have to check this up if it was right-- I think it was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have to check this up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We lost a lot of men there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had to withdraw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then they gave me a week furlough, because it was close to the end of the war, to go to London.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was in the end of April, beginning of May, a week up and down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we liberated the north of Holland, which was the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "To liberate the Hague, sure, it speaks by itself that I was crying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the people were hungry ad starving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know that we had these parachutes coming down with food.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
